# MESSI — Expert-Level Project Documentation
## From Zero to Full Understanding: How It Works, Why It Works, and What Every Piece Does

---

> **Who this document is for:** You — so that if your professor, a peer, or anyone else asks you ANY question about this project, you can answer it confidently and correctly.

