# PART 14: KEY ACADEMIC CONCEPTS REFERENCED

| Concept | Paper / Origin | Where We Use It |
|---------|---------------|-----------------|
| BiLSTM for NER | Lample et al., 2016 | Layer 2 encoder |
| CRF for sequence labeling | Lafferty et al., 2001 | Layer 2 decoder |
| Char-level CNN | Ma & Hovy, 2016 | Character features |
| MC Dropout | Gal & Ghahramani, 2016 | Layer 4 uncertainty |
| Shannon Entropy | Shannon, 1948 | Uncertainty measurement |
| ILP for NLP | Roth & Yih, 2004 | Layer 3 validation |
| Label Smoothing | Szegedy et al., 2016 | Training regularisation |
| Cosine LR Decay | Loshchilov & Hutter, 2017 | LR scheduling |

